  "detailed_description": "The Dark Realm is a bullet hell roguelike with emphasis on fast-paced gameplay. No more boring choices, dialogues and inventory management - just do everything as you go and enjoy the pure action as you try to survive in different environments, find countless items and equipment on your way, but be careful - with enemies around every corner, and occasional all-powerful bosses, it won't be that easy..<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><br>Twelve distinct classes to play, with their unique playstyles and upgradeable abilities!<br><br>Randomly generated equipment and four different procedurally generated areas!<br><br>Over 130 pickup items, thousands of combinations. Keeping each run fresh!<br><br>Two separate gamemodes and four difficulties, so that everyone can enjoy The Dark Realm.<br><br>Infinite replayability and hours of fun (and pain on the higher difficulties)!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>With help of:</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/321e1533dbbb24dde16b1aba17cc6590.poster.avif?t=1733535194\" width=96 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/321e1533dbbb24dde16b1aba17cc6590.webm?t=1733535194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/321e1533dbbb24dde16b1aba17cc6590.mp4?t=1733535194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/58ae4d979011ea923a2309138896d0f9.poster.avif?t=1733535194\" width=96 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/58ae4d979011ea923a2309138896d0f9.webm?t=1733535194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/58ae4d979011ea923a2309138896d0f9.mp4?t=1733535194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>SurferVelocity & bear.mp3",
  "about_the_game": "The Dark Realm is a bullet hell roguelike with emphasis on fast-paced gameplay. No more boring choices, dialogues and inventory management - just do everything as you go and enjoy the pure action as you try to survive in different environments, find countless items and equipment on your way, but be careful - with enemies around every corner, and occasional all-powerful bosses, it won't be that easy..<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><br>Twelve distinct classes to play, with their unique playstyles and upgradeable abilities!<br><br>Randomly generated equipment and four different procedurally generated areas!<br><br>Over 130 pickup items, thousands of combinations. Keeping each run fresh!<br><br>Two separate gamemodes and four difficulties, so that everyone can enjoy The Dark Realm.<br><br>Infinite replayability and hours of fun (and pain on the higher difficulties)!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>With help of:</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/321e1533dbbb24dde16b1aba17cc6590.poster.avif?t=1733535194\" width=96 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/321e1533dbbb24dde16b1aba17cc6590.webm?t=1733535194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/321e1533dbbb24dde16b1aba17cc6590.mp4?t=1733535194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/58ae4d979011ea923a2309138896d0f9.poster.avif?t=1733535194\" width=96 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918790/extras/58ae4d979011ea923a2309138896d0f9.webm?